Study and Research in Germany - you can find these and many other topics at this year ' s German_Education_Fair 2015 on 13/12/15 at Rex_Hotel , HCMC . Numerous_German universities and institutions host this event . Today , we introduce two of them to you :
1 . Berlin_University of Applied_Sciences ( www.htw-berlin.de ) . The HTW Berlin is the biggest university for Applied_Science , therefore , it combines around 70 degree programs in the fields of engineering , computer science , business , culture and design .
2 . Berlin_School of Economics and Law ( www.hwr-berlin.de ) . This university has also 156 partnerships worldwide . It
emphasis on a good link between theory and practics in General_Management_Programs .
For more information visit this year ' s German_Higher_Education_Fair 2015 on 12th and 13th December ( www.daadvn.org/fair ) !
